      <title>Section Learning Objectives</title>
<para id="fs-id1167063466383">By the end of this section, you will be able to do the following:</para>
      <list id="fs-id1167066881433"><item>Describe simple and complex machines</item>
<item>Calculate mechanical advantage and efficiency of simple and complex machines</item>
      </list></note>
    <note id="fs-id1167067034386" class="os-teacher">
      <title>Teacher Support</title>
